# Populate Full Name Plugin

## Overview

The **Populate Full Name Plugin** is a Microsoft Dynamics 365 CRM plugin developed using C#. It automatically populates the **Full Name** field by concatenating the **First Name** and **Last Name** whenever a new record is created.

This project demonstrates the complete plugin development lifecycle, including creating a Class Library, implementing the `IPlugin` interface, building a DLL, registering the plugin, and testing the functionality in Dynamics 365.

---

# Business Requirement

When a user creates a new record:

| Field | Value |
|-------|-------|
| First Name | Sudheer |
| Last Name | Varma |

The plugin should automatically populate:

| Field | Value |
|-------|-------|
| Full Name | Sudheer Varma |

